introduction.stats: was founded on 18th September 1996, with its head office based at 16 Phan Chu Trinh, Hoan Kiem District, Hanoi - with registered capital of VND 4,845 billion, with about 160 branches nationwide, and nearly 4000 employees
introduction.mission: Early since establishment, VIB have always strived to achieve core values in order to bring customers satisfaction and excellent experiences
introduction.partnership: With the strategic partnership of CBA - one of the largest banking system of Australia - and a strategic vision, VIB has been establishing itself among the top commercial joint stock banks  in Vietnam. On the course of development, VIB has constructed strong partnership with reputable partners such as BMW, Mercedes-Benz, Phu My Hung, Prudential Group, etc.  to diversify and  provide the best products and services to customers
introduction.award-2: The leading Vietnamese partner bank of IFC, with its credit line increased by 50%
introduction.award-3: VIB strengthens its top Moody’s B3 rating position in the latest assessment of the 9 local Vietnam
introduction.award-4: Banking market by Moody’s International Rating Agency
introduction.award-5: Among top 5 Government bond traders on Hanoi Stock Exchange
introduction.award-6: MyVIB awarded by IDG for Vietnam's Outstanding Innovative Banking Product/Service Award
introduction.award-7: Among top 10 banks selected to pilot Basel II, VIB is a Bank with the highest capital adequacy ratio (CAR)
